name: The Four Door Hillgate Sideboard
description: The Four door Hillgate is an Art Deco inspired side cabinet with lustrous finishing will inject glamour and style into any room. Finished in any of DAVIDSON's sumptuous timber finishes this cabinet is sure to make a luxury statement. The chamfered edge gives this cabinet intrigue and character with four doors opening to reveal a satin interior with two adjustable shelves within, and additional customisation options for further storage if required. It is smartly elevated off the ground by three plinths exuding Art Deco influence.
